<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 1cm; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f0f0f0; /* Fond gris clair pour faire ressortir la carte blanche */
            color: #1a202c;
        }
        .license-container {
            width: 90mm; 
            height: 58mm;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .top-stripe {
            height: 6px;
            background: #ff6b00;
        }
        .header {
            background: #1a365d;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ff6b00;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 900;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 9px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            opacity: 0.8;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .main-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .photo-area {
            width: 65px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #f7fafc;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .user-details {
            padding-left: 15px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1a365d;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .sub-info {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .info-grid {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .info-item {
            width: 50%;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .label {
            font-size: 7px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        .value {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 55%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-30deg);
            font-size: 45px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: rgba(26, 54, 93, 0.03);
            white-space: nowrap;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .logo-small {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 12px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        .signature-area {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 12px;
            left: 15px;
            width: 110px;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 0.5px solid #a0aec0;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .signature-text {
            font-size: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #718096;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {# Calcul de la validité selon les règles de la FFC #}
    {% set emissionDate = "now"|date('d/m/Y') %}
    {% set currentMonth = "now"|date('n') %}
    {% set currentYear = "now"|date('Y') %}
    
    {# Si souscription à partir de septembre (mois 9), valable jusqu'à la fin de l'année suivante #}
    {% if currentMonth >= 9 %}
        {% set expiryYear = currentYear + 1 %}
    {% else %}
        {% set expiryYear = currentYear %}
    {% endif %}
    {% set expiryDate = "31/12/" ~ expiryYear %}

    <div class="license-container">
        <div class="top-stripe"></div>
        <div class="header">
            {% if logo %}
                <img src="{{ logo }}" class="logo-small" alt="Logo">
            {% endif %}
            <h1>Fédération La Roue Libre</h1>
            <p>Licence Officielle de Compétition BMX</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="watermark">LA ROUE LIBRE</div>

        <div class="content">
            <table class="main-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="photo-area">
                        {% if avatar %}
                            <img src="{{ avatar }}" style="width: 65px; height: 80px; object-fit: cover;" alt="Photo">
                        {% else %}
                            <div style="padding-top: 30px; font-size: 8px; color: #a0aec0;">PHOTO</div>
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                    <td class="user-details">
                        <div class="name">{{ user.firstname }} {{ user.lastname }}</div>
                        <div class="sub-info">Né(e) le {{ user.birthday|date('d/m/Y') }} • {{ licence.nationaly }}</div>
                        
                        <table class="info-grid">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">ID Licence</span>
                                    <span class="value">LR-{{ currentYear }}-{{ licence.id|format('%05d') }}</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Catégorie</span>
                                    <span class="value">{{ licence.priceLicence.label }}</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Émis le</span>
                                    <span class="value">{{ emissionDate }}</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="info-item">
                                    <span class="label">Validité</span>
                                    <span class="value">{{ expiryDate }}</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-area">
            {% if signature %}
                <img src="{{ signature }}" style="height: 30px; margin-bottom: -5px; display: block;" alt="Signature">
            {% endif %}
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div class="signature-text">Signature du titulaire</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Deuxième carte (Verso) -->
    <div class="license-container" style="background: #1a365d; color: white; border: none; margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="content" style="padding: 25px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #ff6b00; text-transform: uppercase;">Informations Importantes</div>
            <div style="font-size: 8px; line-height: 1.5; color: #e2e8f0; text-align: justify;">
                Cette licence est strictement personnelle et doit être présentée sur demande lors des compétitions officielles. 
                Le titulaire s'engage à respecter le règlement de la Fédération La Roue Libre. 
                En cas d'urgence, veuillez contacter les services de secours. 
                Cette carte atteste que le titulaire a fourni un certificat médical valide.
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 15px;">
                {% if user.adresses|length > 0 %}
                    {% set addr = user.adresses|first %}
                    <div style="font-size: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0.9;">
                        Titulaire : {{ addr.number }} {{ addr.type }} {{ addr.label }} {{ addr.cp }} {{ addr.city }}
                    </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: bold;">www.larouelibre.fr</div>
                <div style="font-size: 7px; opacity: 0.6;">© {{ currentYear }} La Roue Libre</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: #ff6b00;"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
